manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: If you meet any problems below when you are using UNBREAKcable iPhone 11/ iPhone XR Screen Protector, UNBREAKcable will send you a New One: Broken/CrackAir bubblesDoesn't fit your phoneMissing Acessories

UNBREAKcable Tempered Glass Screen Protector for iPhone XR / iPhone 11 Q: Why choose UNBREAKcable Premium Tempered Screen Protector for your iPhone XR/ iPhone 11 OLED display? A: Even though Apple describes the OLED glass as its strongest ever on an iPhone, it's still vulnerable to cracks. Unbreakcable 9H Hardness iPhone 11/ iPhone XR Glass Screen Protector enhances shatterproof and extremely scratch-resistant for your phone screen. Q. Is the iPhone 11/ iPhone XR Screen Protector easy to install? A: Yes, UNBREAKcable iPhone 11/ iPhone XR tempered glass protector comes with all accessories needed for a succeddful installation - 1 installation frame, 3 wet cloth, 1 lint-free cloth, 3 dust absorber, 2 dust stickers and detailed installation guide.It is easy to install this bubble-free screen protector. Q: How do I ensure a successful installation with less bubbles and dust? A: Please clean the installation frame with the wet cloth before you align it on the screen. For best results, install the iPhone 11/ iPhone XR screen protector in a clean, dust-free environment. We highly recommend you read the detailed installation guide before you apply it. Q: How do I eliminate bubbles under the screen protector? A: Please following the instructionin the user manual to clean the screen before installing the iPhone 11/ iPhone XR glass screen protector. If there are still any bubbles between the screen protector and the phone screen, use the cloth provided to gently smooth them toward the closest edge of the glass protector.

Q: Does the screen protector show fingerprints? A: Because of the oleophobic coating on our screen protectors, your fingerprints won't readily smudge your screen and if there are any fingerprint smudges, they can be easily wiped away. We recommend using a microfiber cloth for quick and easy cleaning. Please kindly note that: The iPhone XR / iPhone 11 6.1 inch screen is a Curved Edge Screen, so the screen protector has to be smaller than the actual phone screen.This design ensures that this type of screen protector is compatible with most phone cases. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install - watch the YOUTUBE video BEFORE you start!
reviews.reviewText: Wow, this was really easy to install. Please, do yourself a favor and watch the YOUTUBE video a couple of times BEFORE you start!I purchased iPhone 11's for my brother and nephew, who are notorious for breaking screens and phones. To save the headache, I bought (2) cases (it was UAG I believe) and (2) sets of these UNBREAKcable Screen Protector. Each set comes with (3) screen protectors, and believe me, I needed the extra one.I watched the video, but I thought using the sticker after I wiped down the NEW phones was a waste of time and skipped the step. DOH! DON'T DO THAT - use the sticker and re-trace your steps. Dust is tiny, tiny, and monstrous. It snuck on the first phone install, as did bubbles under the glass. Well, because I didn't watch the video close enough - DOH!I tried again, used the stickers, FOLLOWED THE INSTRUCTIONS, and voila! Perfect... looked pristine, clear glass, no bubbles, no worries. The COOLEST thing is that you get it lined up with a guidance thingie, and then you simply TOUCH THE CENTER of the protector, and it attaches like magic. This helps seal out the bubbles, but if you mess up, they have some info on how you can take it off and try again. Just READ AND FOLLOW THE INSTRUCTIONS, unlike I did at first... lol.After I removed the guidance thingie they provided, I smoothed out the edges by using the cloth provided, just to make sure it was connected entirely to the phone. Beautiful... smooth... showroom quality.After both were installed, I put them in their phone cases. If you have to switch out a SIM card, you can hold off on the last part until you've done that step.The rep at the T-Mobile store (went there with them to make sure they were set up, I'm not their phone tech... lol) commented that the screen protectors were perfect. He asked (and maybe you will too) why I bought an extra set.My nephew drops his phone ALL THE TIME. I fully expect him to crack the screen protector at some point. If they have the new ones, they can look online, take off the broken protector, and re-install another one.ANY PROTECTOR CAN BREAK. If it breaks, that means that it has probably protected the actual screen from breaking. I'd rather replace the protectors several times in the life of the phone than replace the phone. He broke his phone so bad last time that it wouldn't ring anymore. That's not very safe... and he didn't want to use a case.Buy a case and use it. Buy these protectors and use them... buy extra! Be sure to get the right size for your phone, and try this particular brand. It's fantastic, and the cost is very reasonable.If this has helped you at all, please give me a HELPFUL vote, and feel free to ask me any questions. Have a great year!

reviews.reviewTitle: Eine hochwertige Schutzfolie für das iPhone 11 und XR
reviews.reviewText: Ich habe vor kurzem das UNBREAKcable Schutzfolien-Set für mein iPhone 11 erworben und bin von der Qualität und Leistung absolut begeistert. Das Paket enthält drei Schutzfolien, was ein großartiges Preis-Leistungs-Verhältnis bietet.Die Installation der Schutzfolie war denkbar einfach. Das Paket enthält eine detaillierte Anleitung sowie alle notwendigen Werkzeuge, um eine blasenfreie Installation zu ermöglichen. Ich war angenehm überrascht, wie einfach und schnell ich die Folie anbringen konnte, ohne dabei lästige Luftblasen oder Staub einzuschließen. Die präzise Passform der Folie für das iPhone 11 und XR ist wirklich beeindruckend.Ein weiterer bemerkenswerter Aspekt der UNBREAKcable Schutzfolie ist ihre Haltbarkeit. Die Folie besteht aus hochwertigem 9H gehärtetem Glas, das einen ausgezeichneten Schutz vor Kratzern, Stößen und Stürzen bietet. Ich habe mein iPhone mehrmals fallen gelassen, und die Schutzfolie hat es erfolgreich vor Beschädigungen bewahrt. Ich bin wirklich beeindruckt von der Widerstandsfähigkeit dieser Folie.Die Schutzfolie beeinträchtigt in keiner Weise die Berührungsempfindlichkeit des Bildschirms. Ich kann mein iPhone weiterhin problemlos bedienen und die Touch-Interaktion ist genauso reibungslos wie zuvor. Darüber hinaus ist die Oberfläche der Folie oleophob beschichtet, was bedeutet, dass Fingerabdrücke und Schmierflecken leicht abgewischt werden können.Was mir besonders gefällt, ist die Klarheit und Transparenz der UNBREAKcable Schutzfolie. Sie beeinträchtigt die Anzeigequalität meines iPhone-Bildschirms nicht und sorgt für eine gestochen scharfe Darstellung. Es gibt auch keine Verzerrungen oder Regenbogeneffekte, die bei minderwertigen Schutzfolien manchmal auftreten können.Zusammenfassend kann ich das UNBREAKcable Schutzfolien-Set für das iPhone 11 und XR nur wärmstens empfehlen. Es bietet eine einfache Installation, hervorragende Haltbarkeit, hervorragenden Schutz und verbesserte Sichtbarkeit.
